name: Gatolm V
description:
Large continents. Large water-filled caves are present just beneath the surface. The plants are tall black stalks covered in red fruit, each with a single circular leaf at the top.

The air is filled with white fluttering creatures. They liquefy instantly when they die.

There are sudden hot winds.


Habitability: 70%
Size: 7
Industry: 3
Science: 3
